hadiths[77]{hadithnumber,text}:
6227,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne Adam ko apni sura par banaya, unki lambai sath hath thi. jab unhein paida kar chuka to farmaya ke jao aur un farishton ko jo baithey huey hain, salam karo aur suno ke tumharey salam ka kya jawab detey hain, kyonke yahi tumhara aur tumhari aulad ka salam hoga. Adam (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Assalaamualaikum ! farishton ne jawab diya, السلام علیک ورحمة الله, unhon-ne Adam ke salam par ''ورحمة الله'' badha diya. to jo shakhs bhi jannat mein jaeyga Adam (Alaihissalam) ki sura ke mutabiq ho kar jaaeyga.'' iske baad se phir khilqat ka qad w qaamat kam hota gaya, ab tak aisa hi hota raha."
6228,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ko qurbani ke din apni sawari par apne peechhey bithaya . wo khoobsurat gorey mard they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko masayel bataaney ke liye khadey ho gaey. usi doran mein qabila Khasam ki aik khoobsurat aurat bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masla poochhney aai. Fazal bhi us aurat ko dekhney lagey. uska husno-jamaal unko bhala malum hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mud kar dekha to Fazal usey dekh rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath peechhey ley ja kar Fazal ki thodii pakdi aur unka chehra dusri taraf kar diya. phir us aurat ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Haj ke barey mein Allah ka jo apne bandon par fareeza hai wo mere walid par laagu hota hai, jo bahut boodhey ho chukey hain aur sawari par seedhey nahi baith saktey. kya agar main unki taraf se Haj kar loon to unka Haj ada ho jaeyga ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, ho jaeyga"
6229,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' raston par baithney se bacho! sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! hamari ye majaalis to bahut zaroori hain, ham wahin roz-marra guftgu kya kartey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha jab tum un majlison mein baithna hi chahtey ho to rastey ka haq ada kya karo yani rastey ko uska haq do. sahaba ne arz kya : rastey ka haq kya hai ya Rasulullah ! farmaya (ghair mehram aurton ko dekhney se) nazar neechi rakhna, raah geeron ko na sataanaa, salam ka jawab denaa, bhalai ka hukm dena aur burai se roknaa."
6230,"jab ham ( shuruaat Islam mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey to kehtey '' salam ho Allah par iske bandon se pahley , salam ho Jibraeel par, salam ho Mikaail par, salam ho falan par, phir (eik martaba ( jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to hamari taraf mutwajjeh ho kar farmaya ke Allah hi salam hai. isliye jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein baithey to التحيات لله ، Mina والصلوات والطيبات Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين padhaa kare. kyonke jab wo ye dua padheyga to aasman w zameen ke har Saleh bandey ko uski ye dua pahunchegii. أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله iske baad usey ikhtiyar hai jo dua chahey padhey ."
6231,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chhotaa badey ko salam karey, guzarney wala baithney waley ko salam karey aur chhoti jamat badi jamat ko pahley salam kare. ''"
6232,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sawaar paidal chalney waley ko salam karey, paidal chalney wala baithey huey ko aur kam tadaad waley badi tadaad walon ko.''"
6233,"mujhey Ziyad ne khabar di, unhein Sabit ne khabar di jo Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid ke ghulam hain. aur unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' sawar paidal chalney waley ko salam karey, paidal chalney wala baithey huey shakhs ko aur chhoti jamat pahley badi jamat ko salam kare. ''"
6234,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chhotaa badey ko salam karey, guzarney wala baithney waley ko aur kam tadaad waley badi tadaad walon ko.''"
6235,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) baton ka hukm diya tha. bimar ki mizaaj-pursii karne ka, janazey ke peechhey chalney ka, chheenkney waley ke jawab dene kaa. kamzor ki madad karne ka, mazloom ki madad karne ka, salam ka jawab dene aur kasrat se salam karne ka, qism ( haq ( khaney waley ki qism poori karne ka, aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ke bartan mein peeney se mana farmaya tha aur soney ki anguthi pahnney se hamein mana farmaya tha. maisar (resham ki zeen) par Sawar honey se, resham aur deebaaj pahnney, qissii (reshamii kapdaa) aur istibraq pahnney se (mana farmaya tha) ."
6236,"aik sahib ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : Islam ki kon si haalat afzal hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye ke) Allah ki makhlooq ko) khana khilaao aur salam karo, usey bhi jisey tum pehchantey ho aur usey bhi jisey nahi pehchantey ."
6237,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke wo apne kisi ( musalman ( bhai se teen din se zyada talluq kaatey ke jab wo milein to ye aik taraf munh pher ley aur doosra dusri taraf aur donon mein achchha wo hai jo salam pahley kare. ''aur Sufiyan ne kaha ke unhon-ne ye hadis Zohri se teen martaba suni hai.
6238,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra ( hijrat karke ( tashrif laey to unki umr das saal thi. phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi ke baqi das saalon mein aap ki khidmat ki aur main parda ke hukm ke mutaalliq sabse zyada janta hun ke Kab nazil hua tha. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se iske barey mein puchha kartey they. parda ke hukm ka nuzool sabse pahley us raat hua jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se nikah ke baad unke sath pehli raat guzari thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke dulhaa they aur aap ne sahaba ko dawat walima par bulaya tha. khaney se farigh ho kar sab log chaley gaey lekin chand aadmi aap ke paas baithey reh gaey aur bahut der tak wahin thahrey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uth kar bahar tashrif le gaey aur main bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chala gaya taake wo log bhi chaley jaaein. Nabi Karim chaltey rahe aur main bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chalta raha aur samjha ke wo log ab chaley gaey hain. isliye wapas tashrif laey aur main bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wapas aaya lekin aap jab Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey mein dakhil huey to wo log abhi baithey huey they aur abhi tak wapas nahi gaey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara wahan se lot gaey aur main bhi aap ke sath lot gaya. jab aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ki chaukhat tak pahunchey to aap ne samjha ke wo log nikal chukey hongey. phir aap lot kar aaey aur main bhi aap ke sath lot aaya to waqei wo log ja chukey they. phir parde ki aayat nazil hui aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere aur apne darmyan parda latkaa liya.
6239,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to log andar aaey aur khana khaya phir baith ke baatein kartey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah izhar kya maano aap khadey hona chahtey hain. lekin wo khadey nahi huey jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dekha to khadey ho gaey. aap ke khadey honey par qaum ke jin logon ko khada hona tha wo bhi khadey ho gaey lekin kuchh log ab bhi baithey rahe aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar dakhil honey ke liye tashrif laey to kuchh log baithey huey they (aap wapas ho gaey (aur phir jab wo log bhi khadey huey aur chaley gaey to maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski itlaa di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur andar dakhil ho gaey. maine bhi andar jana chaha lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere aur apne darmyan parda daal liya aur Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي ''aey eman waalo! Nabi ke ghar mein na dakhil ho.'' aakhir tak.
6240,umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) paak beeviyon ka parda karaaein. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa nahi kya aur paak beeviyan zarurat se farigh honey ke liye sirf raat hi ke waqt nikalti thin (us waqt gharon mein baitul-khala nahi they) aik martaba Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) bahar gaee hui thin. unka qad lamba tha. Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekha. us waqt wo majlis mein baithey huey they. unhon-ne kaha Sauda maine aapko pehchan liya ye unhon-ne isliye kaha kyonke wo parda ke hukm nazil honey ke badey mutmannii they. bayan kya ke phir Allah Taala ne parde ki aayat nazil ki.
6241,"aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kisi hujre mein suraakh se dekha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas us waqt aik kangha tha jis se aap sar Mubarak khujaa rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke agar mujhey malum hota ke tum jhank rahe ho to ye kangha tumhari aankh mein chubho deta (andar dakhil honey se pahley) ijazat maangna to hai hi isliye ke (andar ki koi zaatii cheez) na dekhi jaey."
6242,"aik sahib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kisi hujre mein jhank kar dekhney lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki taraf teer ka phal ya bahut se phal lekar badhey, maano main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh raha hun un sahib ki taraf is tarah chupkey-chupkey tashrif laey."
6243,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis se zyada sagheera gunahon se mushabeh (similar) maine aur koi cheez nahi dekhi. (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo baatein bayan ki hain wo murad hain) mujh se Mehmood ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdur-Razzaq ne khabar di, kaha ham ko Mamar ne khabar di, unhein ibne- Taaus ne, unhein unke walid ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke maine koi cheez sagheera gunahon se mushabeh (similar) is hadis ke muqable mein nahi dekhi jisey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya hai ke Allah Taala ne insanon ke maamle mein zina mein se iska hissey likh diya hai jis se wo laa-muhaalaa do-chaar hoga to aankh ka zina dekhnaa hai, zaban ka zina bolnaa hai, dil ka zina ye hai ke wo khahish aur aarzoo karta hai phir sharmgah us khahish ko sachcha karti hai ya jhutlaa deti hai."
6244,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi ko salam kartey (aur jawab na miltaa) to teen martaba salam kartey they aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi baat farmatey to (zyaada se zyaada) teen martaba usey dohraatey.
6245,"mein Ansar ki aik majlis mein tha ke abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey jaisey ghabraaey huey hon. unhon-ne kaha ke maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan teen martaba andar aaney ki ijazat chahi lekin mujhey koi jawab nahi mila, isliye wapas chala aaya ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum hua) to unhon-ne malum kya ke (andar aaney mein) kya baat rukawat thi? maine kaha ke maine teen martaba andar aaney ki ijazat mangi aur jab mujhey koi jawab nahi mila to wapas chala gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke jab tum mein se koi kisi se teen martaba ijazat chahey aur ijazat na miley to wapas chala jana chahiye umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumhen is hadis ki sihat ke liye koi gawah lana hoga. ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne majlis walon se puchha ( kya tum mein koi aisa hai jisne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni ho? Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! tumharey sath ( uski gawahi dene ke siwa ( jamat mein sabse kam Umr shakhs ke koi aur nahi khada hoga. abu-Saeed ne kaha aur main hi jamat ka wo sabse kam Umr aadmi tha mein unke sath uth khada ho gaya aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke waqei Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa farmaya hai. aur ibne-Mubarak ne bayan kya ke mujh ko Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne khabar di, kaha mujh se Yazeed bin khaseefa ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, kaha maine abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se suna phir yahi hadis naql ki."
6246,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (aap ke ghar mein) dakhil hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik badey pyaley mein doodh paya to farmaya '' Abu-Hurera ! ahal suffa ke paas ja aur unhein mere paas bula laa. main unke paas aaya aur unhein bula laya. wo aaey aur (andar aaney ki) ijazat chahi phir jab ijazat di gaee to dakhil huey. ''
6247,aap bachchon ke paas se guzrey to unhein salam kya aur farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi aisa hi kartey they.
6248,ham Juma ke din khush hua kartey they. maine kaha kis liye? farmaya ke hamari aik budhiyaa thin jo maqam bizaa' jaya karti thin. ibne-Salma ne kaha ke Bizaa' Madina Munawra ka khajoor ka aik baagh tha. phir wo wahan se chuqandar laya karti thin aur usey handi mein dalti thin aur jau ke kuchh daney pees kar (is mein milaatii thiin) jab ham Juma ki Namaz padh kar wapas hotey to unhein salam karne aatey aur wo ye chuqandar ki jad mein aata mili hui dawat hamarey samney rakhti thin ham us wjah se Juma ke din khush hua kartey they aur qailula ya do-pahar ka khana ham Juma ke baad kartey they.
6249,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Aaisha! ye Jibraeel hain tumhen salam kehtey hain bayan kya ke maine arz kya وعليه السلام ورحمة الله aap dekhtey hain jo ham nahi dekh saktey Ummul-Momenin ka ishara Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf tha. Mamar ke sath us hadis ko Shuaib aur Yunus aur Nauman ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai Yunus aur Nauman ki riwayaton main ( وبركاته‏ .) ka lafz zyada hai.
6250,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein us qarz ke barey mein hazir hua jo mere walid par tha. maine darwaza khatkhataayaa . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kon hain? maine kaha ''main '' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' main, main '' jaisey aap ne us jawab ko na-pasand farmaya,"
6251,"aik shakhs masjid mein dakhil hua, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid ke kinarey baithey huey they. us ne Namaz padhi aur phir hazir ho kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wa'lekassalaam wapas ja aur dobara Namaz padh , kyonke tum ne Namaz nahi padhi. wo wapas gaey aur Namaz padhi. phir (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke paas aaey aur salam kya aap ne farmaya wa'lekassalaam. wapas jao phir Namaz padho . kyonke tum ne Namaz nahi padhi. wo wapas gaya aur us ne phir Namaz padhi. phir wapas aaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein salam arz kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab mein farmaya wa'laikassalaam. wapas jao aur dobara Namaz padho . kyonke tum ne Namaz nahi padhi. un sahib ne dusri martaba , ya iske ba'd, arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mujhey Namaz padhni sikhaa dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz ke liye khadey hua karo to pahley poori tarah wuzu kya karo, phir qibley ki taraf ho kar takbeer ( takbeer tahreema ( kaho , iske baad Quran Majeed mein se jo tumharey liye aasan ho wo padho, phir rukoo karo aur jab rukoo ki haalat mein barabar ho jao to sar uthaao. jab seedhey khadey ho jao to phir sajde mein jao, jab sajda poori tarah kar lo to sar uthao aur achi tarah se baith jao phir sajde mein jao, jab sajda poori tarah kar lo to sar uthao aur achi tarah se baith jao. yahi amal apni har rakaat mein karo aur abu-Usama (raawii) ne baad yun kaha ke phir utho yahan tak ke saiyed hai khada ho jao ."
6252,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' phir sar sajde se utha aur achi tarah baith jaa. ''
6253,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) tumhen salam kehtey hain. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke w-alaihissalaam warahmatullaah un par bhi Allah ki taraf se salamati aur uski rehmat nazil ho.
6254,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik gadhey par Sawar huey jis par paalaan bandhaa hua tha aur nichey fidak ki bani hui aik makhmalii chadar bichhi hui thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sawari par apne peechhey Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko bithaya tha. aap bani Haris bin khazraj mein Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe they. ye jange-badr se pahley ka waqia hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik majlis par se guzrey jis mein musalmaan, but parast, mushrik aur Yahudi sab hi Sharik they. Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool bhi unmein tha. majlis mein Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha bhi maujood they. jab majlis par sawari ki gard padi to Abdullah ne apni chadar se apni naak chipa li aur kaha ke hamarey uper ghubaar na udaao . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam kya aur wahan ruk gaey aur utar kar unhein Allah ki taraf bulaya aur unke liye Quran Majeed ki tilawat ki. Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool bola, miyan ye baatein meri samajh mein nahiin aatiin agar wo cheez haq hai jo tum kehtey ho to hamari majlison mein aa kar hamein takleef na diya karo. is par ibne- Rawaha ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap hamari majlison mein tashrif laya karein kyonke ham usey pasand kartey hain. phir muslmaanon, mushrikon aur yahudiyon mein is baat par tu-tu main-main honey lagi aur qareeb tha ke wo koi irada kar baithein aur aik doosrey par hamla kar dein. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein barabar khamosh karatey rahe aur jab wo khamosh ho gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par baith kar Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, Sad tum ne nahi suna ke abu-Hubaab ne aaj kya baat kahi hai. aap ka ishara Abdullah-bin-Ubai ki taraf tha ke usne ye ye baatein kahi hain. Sad ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! usey maaf kar dijiye aur darguzar farmaiye. Allah Taala ne wo haq aapko ata farmaya hai jo ata farmana tha. us basti (Madina munawwara) ke log (aap ki tashrif aawrii se pahley) is par muttafiq ho gaey they ke usey taaj pehna dein aur shahi amama uske sar par baandh dein lekin jab Allah Taala ne us mansubey ko us haq ki wjah se khatm kar diya jo usney aapko ata farmaya hai to usey haq se hasad ho gaya aur usi wjah se us ne ye mamla kya hai jo aap ne dekha. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey maaf kar diya."
6255,"jab wo jange-Tabook mein Sharik nahi ho sakey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se baat-cheet karne ki manaahii kar di thi aur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar salam karta tha aur ye andaza lagata tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab salam mein hont Mubarak hilaaey ya nahi, aakhir pachaas din guzar gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki bargah mein hamari tauba ke qabool kiye janey ka namaze-Fajr ke baad elaan kya."
6256,"kuchh Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke) السام عليك‏) ( tumhen maut aaey ( mein unki baat samajh gaee aur maine jawab diya ( عليكم السام واللعنة‏ . Mina ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aaisha sabr se kaam ley kyonke Allah Taala tamam maamlaat mein narmii ko pasand karta hai, maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ne nahi suna ke unhon-ne kya kaha tha? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine unko jawab de diya tha ke) Waalekum ( (aur tumhen bhi) ."
6257,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab tumhen Yahudi salam karein aur agar unmein se koi ( السام عليك‏ . Mina ( kahey to tum iske jawab mein sirf ( وعليك ( (aur tumhen bhi) keh diya karo.
6258,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab ahle-kitab tumhen salam karein to tum iske jawab mein sirf ( Waalekum ( kaho. ''
6259,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Zubair-bin-Awaam aur Abu-Marsad ghanwii ko bhejaa. ham sab ghud sawar they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur jab rauza khaakh (Makka aur Madina ke darmyan aik maqam ( par pahuncho to wahan tumhen mushrekeen ki aik aurat milegii uske paas Haatib bin abi Balta' ka aik khat hai jo mushrekeen ke paas bheja gaya hai (usey ley aao). bayan kya ke ham ne us aurat ko pa liya wo apne oont par ja rahi thi aur wahin par mili (jahaan) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bataya tha. bayan kya ke ham ne us se kaha ke khat jo tum sath ley ja rahi ho wo kahan hai? usne kaha ke mere paas koi khat nahi hai. ham ne iske oont ko bithaya aur uske kajaawe mein talashi li lekin hamein koi cheez nahi milii. mere donon sathiyon ne kaha ke hamein koi khat to nazar aata nahi. bayan kya ke maine kaha, mujhey yaqin hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghalat baat nahi kahi hai. qism hai uski jiski qism khaaii jati hai, tum khat nikaalo warna main tumhen nangaa kar doonga . bayan kya ke jab us aurat ne dekha ke main waqei us maamle mein sanjeeda hun to usne izaar baandhney ki jagah ki taraf hath badhaayaa, wo aik chadar izaar ke taur par baandhey huey thi aur khat nikaalaa. bayan kya ke ham usey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Haatib tum ne aisa kyon kya? unhon-ne kaha ke main ab bhi Allah aur uske rasool par eman rakhta hun. mere andar koi badlaaw w tabdili nahi aai hai, mera maqsad ( khat bhejney se) sirf ye tha ke) Quraish par aap ki fauj kashii ki itlaa dun aur us tarah) mera un logon par ehsan ho jaey aur uski wjah se Allah mere ahal aur maal ki taraf se ( unse ( mudaafiat karaaey. aap ke jitney muhajir sahaba hain unke Makka Mukarrama mein aisey afraad hain jinke zariey Allah unke maal aur unke ghar walon ki hifazat karaaeyga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne sach keh diya hai ab tum log unke barey mein siwa bhalai ke aur kuchh na kaho bayan kya ke is par umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke us shakhs ne Allah aur uske rasool aur mominon ke sath khayanat ki, mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uski gardan mar dun bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : umr ! tumhen kya ma'loom, Allah Taala badr ki ladai mein Sharik sahaba ki zindagi par muttla tha aur uske bawajud farmaya ke tum jo chaho karo, tumharey liye jannat likh di gaee hai, bayan kya ke is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhon mein aansu aagey aur arz kya : Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jaanney waley hain."
6260,"Hiraql ne Quraish ke chand afraad ke sath unhein bhi bula bheja ye log Sham (Syria) tijarat ki gharaz se gaey they sab log Hiraql ke paas aaey phir unhon-ne waqia bayan kya ke phir Hiraql ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khat mangwaya aur wo padha gaya khat mein ye likha hua thaa. bismillaahir-rahmaanir-raheem, Muhammad ki taraf se jo Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hai (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . Hiraql azeem Rome (mojooda Itly) ki taraf, salam ho un par jinhoney hidayat ki ittaba (pairvi) ki. ammaa ba'd!"
6261,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ke aik shakhs ka zikr kya ke unhon-ne lakdi ka aik latthaa liya aur is mein suraakh karke aik hazaar Dinar aur khat rakh diya wo unki taraf se unke sathi ( qarz-khaah ( ki taraf tha aur Umar-bin abi Salma ne bayan kya ke unse unke walid ne aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne lakdi ke aik latthey mein suraakh kya aur maal iske andar rakh diya aur unke paas aik khat likha , falan ki taraf se falan ko miley."
6262,Qureza ke Yahudi Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko saalis banaaney par taiyaar ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bula bheja jab wo aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne sardaar ke leney ko utho ya yun farmaya ke apne mein sabse behtar ko leney ke liye utho. phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baith gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bani Qureza ke log tumharey faisley par razi ho kar) qil'a se) utar aaey hain ( ab tum kya faisla kartey ho ( . Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir main ye faisla karta hun ke unmein jo jang ke qaabil hain unhein qatl kar diya jaey aur unke bachchon aur aurton ko qaid kar liya jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aap ne wahi faisla farmaya jis faisla ko farishta lekar aaya tha. abu-Adbullah ( musannif ( ne bayan kya ke mujhey mere kuchh ashaab ne abul-Waleed ke waaste se abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul ( alii (ke bajaey بصلہ ( إلى حكمك‏ . Mina ( naql kya hai.
6263,"maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya musaafa ka dastoor Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein tha? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan zaroor tha."
6264,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath pakdey huey they.
6265,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey tashahud sikhaayaa, us waqt mera hath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hatheliyon ke darmyan mein tha (is tarah sikhaayaa) jis tarah aap Quran ki sura sikhaya kartey they. التحيات لله والصلوات والطيبات ، Mina Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين ، Mina أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt hayaat they. jab aap ki wafat ho gaee to ham ( Khattab ka seegha ke bajaey) is tarah padhney lagey السلام‏ . Mina على النبي yaanii Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par salam ho."
6266,"Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) (marzul-maut mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se nikley (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se Ahmed bin Saleh ne bayan kya, kaha ham se anbasaa bin Khalid ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yunus bin Yazeed ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Shahab Zohri ne bayan kya, kaha mujh ko Abdullah-bin Kab-bin-Malik ne khabar di aur unhein Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan se nikley, ye us marz ka waqia hai jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui thi. logon ne puchha : aey abul-Hasan! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah kaisi guzaarii? unhon-ne kaha ke bihamdillaah aapko sukoon raha hai. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne pakad kar kaha, kya tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhtey nahi ho. ( Allah ki qism ( teen din ke baad tumhen laathii ka banda bannaa padega. Allah ki qism main samajhta hun ke is marz mein aap wafat pa jaengey. main bani abdul-Muttalib ke chehron par maut ke aasaar ko khub pehchanta hun, isliye hamarey sath tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chalo. taake puchha jaey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad khilafat kis ke hath mein rahegi agar wo hamiin logon ko miltii hai to hamein malum ho jaeyga aur agar dusron ke paas jaeygi to ham arz karengey taake Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey barey mein kuchh wasiiyat karein. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! agar ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khilafat ki darkhaast ki aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kar diya to phir log hamein kabhi nahi dengey main to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kabhi nahi poochhunga ke aap ke baad kon khaleefa ho."
6267,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey sawar tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Muaz ! maine kaha ( لبيك وسعديك‏ . Mina ( ) hazir hun) . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba mujhey isi tarah mukhaatab kya iske baad farmaya tumhen malum hai ke bandon par Allah ka kya haq hai? (phir khud hi jawab diyaa) ye ke usi ki ibadat karein aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehraein phir aap thodi der chaltey rahe aur farmaya ke aey Muaaz! maine kaha ( لبيك وسعديك‏ ( farmaya tumhen malum hai ke jab wo ye kar lein to Allah par bandon ka kya haq hai? ye ke unhein azab na de.
6268,"(kaha ke) Allah ki qism ham se Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne maqam Rabza mein bayan kya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath raat ke waqt Madina Munawra ki kali pattharon wali zameen par chal raha tha ke Uhud pahaad dikhai diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey abu-Zar! mujhey pasand nahi ke agar Uhud pahaad ke barabar bhi mere paas sona ho aur mujh par aik raat bhi is tarah guzar jaey ya teen raat ke usmein se aik Dinar bhi mere paas baqi bachey. siwaey iske jo main qarz ki adaaeygi ke liye mehfooz rakh loon main us sarey soney ko Allah ki makhlooq mein is-is tarah taqseem kar doonga. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski kaifiyat hamein apne hath se lap bhar kar dikhaaii. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Abu-Zar ! maine arz kya ( لبيك وسعديك‏ . Mina (ya Rasulullah! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zyada jama karne waley hi (sawab ki haisiyat se) kam hasil karne waley hongey. siwaey iske jo Allah ke bandon par maal is-is tarah yani kasarat ke sath kharch kare. phir farmaya yahin thahrey raho abu-Zar! yahan se us waqt tak na hatna jab tak mein wapas na aa jaun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif le gaey aur nazron se ojhal ho gaey. iske baad maine awaz suni aur mujhey khatrah hua ke kahin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi pareshani na pesh aa gaee ho. isliye maine (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhney ke liye) jana chaha lekin fauran hi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad yad aaya ke yahan se na hatnaa. chunanche main wahin ruk gaya (jab aap tashrif laey to ( maine arz ki. maine awaz suni thi aur mujhey khatrah ho gaya tha ke kahin aapko koi pareshani na pesh aa jaey phir mujhey aap ka irshad yad aaya isliye main yahin thahar gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they. mere paas aaey they aur mujhey khabar di hai ke meri ummat ka jo shakhs bhi is haal mein marega ke Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thahraataa ho to wo jannat mein jaeyga maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! bhale hi usne zina aur chori ki ho? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, agar us ne zina aur chori bhi ki ho. (Aamash ne bayan kya ke) maine Zaid-bin Wahab se kaha ke mujhey malum hua hai ke is hadis ke rawi abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) hain? Zaid ne farmaya main gawahi deta hun ke ye hadis mujh se Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne maqam Rabza mein bayan ki thi. Aamash ne bayan kya ke mujh se Abu-Saleh ne hadis bayan ki aur unse abu darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah bayan kya aur abu-shahaab ne Aamash se bayan kya."
6269,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs kisi doosrey shakhs ko iske baithney ki jagah se na uthaey ke khud wahan baith jaaey.''
6270,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya tha ke kisi shakhs ko uski jagah se uthaya jaey taake doosra uski jagah par baithey, albatta ( aaney waley ko majlis mein) jagah de diya karo aur faraakhii kar diya karo aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) na-pasand kartey they ke koi shakhs majlis mein se kisi ko utha kar khud uski jagah baith jaey."
6271,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to logon ko) dawat walima par) bulaya. logon ne khana khaya phir baith kar baatein kartey rahe bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kya maano aap uthna chahtey hain. lekin log ( phir bhi baithey huey they) phir bhi khadey nahi huey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dekha to aap khadey ho gaey jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey to aap ke sath aur bhi bahut se sahaba khadey ho gaey lekin teen aadmi ab bhi baqi reh gaey. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar janey ke liye tashrif laey lekin wo log ab bhi baithey huey they. iske baad wo log bhi chaley gaey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main aaya aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa di ke wo ( teen aadmi ( bhi ja chukey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur andar dakhil ho gaey. maine bhi andar jana chaha lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere aur apne darmyan parda daal liya aur Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي إلا أن يؤذن لكم aey eman waalo! Nabi ke ghar mein us waqt tak dakhil na ho jab tak tumhen ijazat na di jaaey.'' irshad hua إن ذلكم كان عند الله عظيما tak.
6272,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sehan Kaba mein dekha ke aap peeth ke bal baithey huey donon raanein pet se milaaey huey hathon se pindlii pakdey huey baithey they.
6273,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya main tumhen sabse badey gunah ki khabar na dun. '' sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya kyon nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke sath shirk karna aur waalidain ki nafarmani karnaa."""
6274,"(aur ye bhi bayan kya ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tek lagaey huey they phir aap seedhey baith gaey aur farmaya '' haan aur jhooti baat bhii. '' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey itni martaba baar-baar dohraatey rahe ke ham ne kaha, kash! aap khamosh ho jatey."
6275,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Asr ki Namaz padhai aur phir badi tezi ke sath chal kar aap ghar mein dakhil ho gaey.
6276,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takht ke beech mein Namaz padhtey they aur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur qible ke darmyan leti rehti thi mujhey koi zarurat hoti lekin mujh ko khadey ho kar aap ke samney aana bura malum hota. albatta aap ki taraf rukh karke main aahista se khisak jati thi.
6277,"main tumharey walid Zaid ke sath Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, unhon-ne ham se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mere rozey ka zikr kya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey maine aap ke liye chamdey ka aik gaddaa, jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi bichhaa diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zameen par baithey aur gaddaa mere aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan waisaa hi padaa raha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke kya tumharey liye har mahiney mein teen din ke) rozey ( kafi nahi ? maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir panch din rakha kar. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! farmaya saat (7) din . maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! farmaya nau (9) din . maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! farmaya gyara (11) din . maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! farmaya Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey se zyada koi roza nahi hai. zindagi ke aadhey din, aik din ka roza aur aik din baghair roza ke rehna."
6278,"aap mulk Sham (Syria) mein pahunchey (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke aur mujh se abul-Waleed ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Mughira ne aur unse Ibrahim ne bayan kya ke Alqama mulk Sham (Syria) gaey aur masjid mein ja kar do rakaat Namaz padhi phir ye dua ki aey Allaah! mujhey aik sathi ata farmaa. chunanche wo abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein ja baithey. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum kya. tumhara talluq kahan se hai? kaha ke ahale-koofa se, puchha kya tumharey yahan (nifaaq aur munaafeqeen ke) bhedon ke jaanney waley wo sahabi nahi hain jinke siwa koi aur unko janta nahi hai? unka ishara Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. kya tumharey yahan wo nahi hain (ya yun kaha ke) tumharey wo jinhein Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zabani shaitan se panah di thi? ishara Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. kya tumharey yahan miswak aur gaddey waley nahi hain? unka ishara ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sura ( والليل إذا يغشى‏ ( kis tarah padhtey they. Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo ( والذكر والأنثى‏ ( padhtey they. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke ye log Kufa waley apne musalsal amal se qareeb tha ke mujhey shubeh mein daal detey halanke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khud usey suna tha."
6279,ham khana aur qailula Namaz Juma ke baad kya kartey they.
6280,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko koi naam abu-Turaab se zyada mahboob nahi tha. jab unko us naam se bulaya jata to wo khush hotey they. aik martaba Rasulullah (sl), Fatima (Alaihissalam) ke ghar tashrif laey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghar mein nahi paya to farmaya ke beti tumharey chacha ke ladkey (aur shauhar) kahan gaey hain? unhon-ne kaha mere aur unke darmyan kuchh talkh kalaamii ho gaee thi wo mujh par ghussa ho kar bahar chaley gaey aur mere yahan ( ghar mein) qailula nahi kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs se kaha ke dekho wo kahan hain. wo sahabi wapas aaey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! wo to masjid mein soey huey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) letey huey they aur chadar aap ke pahlu se gir gaee thi aur gard mein ho gaee thi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se mitti saaf karne lagey aur farmaney lagey, abu-Turaab! (mittii waale) utho, abu-Turaab! utho."
6281,"(unki waalida) Umme-Sulaim, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye chamdey ka farsh bichhaa deti thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan usi par qailula kar letey they. bayan kya phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey (aur bedaar huey) to Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka paseena aur (jhadey huey) aap ke baal ley liye aur (paseena ko) aik sheeshii mein jama kya aur phir ( سك ( (eik khushboo) mein usey mila liya. bayan kya hai ke phir jab Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt qareeb hua to unhon-ne wasiiyat ki ke us ( سك ( (jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka paseena mila hua tha) mein se unke Hanoot mein mila diya jaey. bayan kya hai ke phir unke Hanoot mein usey milaya gaya."
6282,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quba tashrif ley jatey they, to umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar bhi jatey they aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khana khilaatii thin phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur bedaar huey to aap hans rahe they. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke rastey mein jang kartey huey mere samney ( khuwab mein) pesh kiye gaey, jo us samandar ke uper (kashtiyon mein) sawar hongey ( jannat mein wo aisey nazar aaey ( jaisey badshah takht par hotey hain, ya bayan kya ke baadshaahon ki tarah takht par. Ishaq ko un lafzon mein zara shuba tha (umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! dua karein ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se banaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar rakh kar so gaey aur jab bedaar huey to hans rahe they. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke raaste mein jang kartey huey mere samney pesh kiye gaey jo us samandar ke uper sawar hongey jaisey badshah takht par hotey hain ya baadshaahon ki tarah takht par. maine arz kya ke Allah se mere liye dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to us giroh ke sabse pahley logon mein hogi chunanche umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki Sham (Syria) par governary ke zamane mein) samandari safar kya aur khushkii par utarney ke baad apni sawari se gir padiin aur wafat pa gain ."
6283,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quba tashrif ley jatey they, to umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar bhi jatey they aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khana khilaatii thin phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur bedaar huey to aap hans rahe they. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke rastey mein jang kartey huey mere samney ( khuwab mein) pesh kiye gaey, jo us samandar ke uper (kashtiyon mein) sawar hongey ( jannat mein wo aisey nazar aaey ( jaisey badshah takht par hotey hain, ya bayan kya ke baadshaahon ki tarah takht par. Ishaq ko un lafzon mein zara shuba tha (umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! dua karein ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se banaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar rakh kar so gaey aur jab bedaar huey to hans rahe they. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke raaste mein jang kartey huey mere samney pesh kiye gaey jo us samandar ke uper sawar hongey jaisey badshah takht par hotey hain ya baadshaahon ki tarah takht par. maine arz kya ke Allah se mere liye dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to us giroh ke sabse pahley logon mein hogi chunanche umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki Sham (Syria) par governary ke zamane mein) samandari safar kya aur khushkii par utarney ke baad apni sawari se gir padiin aur wafat pa gain ."
6284,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 tarah ke pahnaawey se aur 2 tarah ki khareed w farokht se mana farmaya tha. ishtimaale-Sammaa (ek chadar ko is tarah lapetna ki jism ka ek hissey khula reh jaaye) aur aik kapdey mein is tarah ehtibaa karne se ke insan ki sharmgah par koi cheez na ho aur mulaamisat aur munaabizat se. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Mamar , Muhammad-bin abi Hafsa aur Abdullah-bin Budail ne Zohri se ki hai."
6285,"ye tamam paak beeviyon (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wafat k marz mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas thin, koi wahan se nahi hata tha ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) chaltii hui aaein. Allah ki qasam! unki chaal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki chaal se alag nahi thi ( balke bahut hi mushabeh (similar) thi) jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to khush aamadeed kaha, farmaya beti ! marhaba ! phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni daain taraf ya baain taraf unhein bithaya . iske baad aahista se unse kuchh kaha aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bahut zyada roney lagiin. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka gham dekha to dobara unse sargoshi ki is par wo hansney lagiin. tamam beeviyon mein se maine unse kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham mein sirf aapko sargoshi ki khusoosiyat bakhshii. phir aap roney lagiin. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey to maine unse puchha ke aap ke kaan mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya tha unhon-ne kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka raaz nahi khol saktii. phir jab aap ki wafat ho gaee to maine Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke mera jo haq aap par hai iska waasta deti hun ke aap mujhey wo baat bata dein. unhon-ne kaha ke ab bata sakti hun, chunanche unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se pehli sargoshi ki thi to farmaya tha ke '' Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) har saal mujh se saal mein aik martaba daur kya kartey they lekin is saal mujh se unhon-ne 2 martaba daur kya aur mera khayal hai ke meri wafat ka waqt qareeb hai, Allah se dartii rehna aur sabr karna kyonke main tumharey liye aik achchha aagey janey wala hun '' bayan kya ke us waqt mera ronaa jo aap ne dekha tha uski wjah yahi thi. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri pareshani dekhi to aap ne dobara mujh se sargoshi ki, farmaya ''Faatima betii! kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke jannat main tum mominon ki aurton ki sardaar hogi, ya (farmaayaa ke) is ummat ki aurton ki sardaar hogii.''"
6286,"ye tamam paak beeviyon (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wafat k marz mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas thin, koi wahan se nahi hata tha ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) chaltii hui aaein. Allah ki qasam! unki chaal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki chaal se alag nahi thi ( balke bahut hi mushabeh (similar) thi) jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to khush aamadeed kaha, farmaya beti ! marhaba ! phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni daain taraf ya baain taraf unhein bithaya . iske baad aahista se unse kuchh kaha aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bahut zyada roney lagiin. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka gham dekha to dobara unse sargoshi ki is par wo hansney lagiin. tamam beeviyon mein se maine unse kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham mein sirf aapko sargoshi ki khusoosiyat bakhshii. phir aap roney lagiin. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey to maine unse puchha ke aap ke kaan mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya tha unhon-ne kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka raaz nahi khol saktii. phir jab aap ki wafat ho gaee to maine Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ke mera jo haq aap par hai iska waasta deti hun ke aap mujhey wo baat bata dein. unhon-ne kaha ke ab bata sakti hun, chunanche unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se pehli sargoshi ki thi to farmaya tha ke '' Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) har saal mujh se saal mein aik martaba daur kya kartey they lekin is saal mujh se unhon-ne 2 martaba daur kya aur mera khayal hai ke meri wafat ka waqt qareeb hai, Allah se dartii rehna aur sabr karna kyonke main tumharey liye aik achchha aagey janey wala hun '' bayan kya ke us waqt mera ronaa jo aap ne dekha tha uski wjah yahi thi. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri pareshani dekhi to aap ne dobara mujh se sargoshi ki, farmaya ''Faatima betii! kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke jannat main tum mominon ki aurton ki sardaar hogi, ya (farmaayaa ke) is ummat ki aurton ki sardaar hogii.''"
6287,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein chit letey dekha aap aik paon doosrey par rakhey huey they.
6288,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab teen aadmi sath hon to teesrey sathi ko chhod kar do aapas mein kaana phoosii (sargoshi) na karein.''
6289,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se aik raaz ki baat kahi thi aur maine wo raaz kisi ko nahi bataya (unki walida ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi mujh se iske mutaalliq puchha lekin maine unhein bhi nahi bataya.
6290,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab teen aadmi hon to teesrey sathi ko chhod kar tum aapas mein kaana phoosii (sargoshi) na kya karo. isliye ke logon ko ranj hoga albatta agar doosrey aadmi bhi hon to muzaayqa nahi.''
6291,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba kuchh maal taqseem farmaya is par Ansar ke aik shakhs ne kaha ke ye aisi taqseem hai jis se Allah ki khushnoodii maqsud na thi maine kaha ke haan! Allah ki qism main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jaaunga. chunanche main gaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt majlis mein baithey huey they maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kaan mein chupkey se ye baat kahi to aap ghussa ho gaey aur aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya phir aap ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) par Allah ki rehmat ho unhein us se bhi zyada takleef pahunchai gaee lekin unhon-ne sabr kya (isliye main bhi sabr karunga) ."
6292,"Namaz ki takbeer kahi gaee aur aik sahabi rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sargoshi kartey rahe, phir wo der tak sargoshi kartey rahe yahan tak ke aap ke sahaba soney lagey iske baad aap uthey aur Namaz padhai."
6293,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab soney lago to ghar mein aag na chhodo.''
6294,Madina Munawra mein aik ghar raat ke waqt jal gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq kaha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aag tumhari dushman hai is liye jab soney lago to usey bujhaa diya karo.
6295,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(sotey waqt) bartan dhak liya karo warna darwazey band kar liya karo aur charagh bujhaa liya karo kyonke ye choohaa kabhi-kabhi charagh ki battii kheench leta hai aur ghar walon ko jalaa deta hai.''
6296,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab raat mein soney lago to charagh bujhaa diya karo aur darwazey band kar liya karo aur mishkezon ka munh baandh diya karo aur khaney peeney ki cheezein dhak diya karo. Hammad ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye bhi farmaya ke '' bhale hi aik lakdi se ho.''
6297,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''paanch cheezein fitrat se hain, khatna karnaa, naaf ke nichey ke baal banaanaa, baghl ke baal saaf karnaa, moonchh chhoti karaanaa aur naakhun kaatna .''"
6298,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ne assii ( 80 ( saal ki umr mein khatna karaya aur aap ne ( qudoom Mina . Mina ( ) kami ke saath) ( kulhaadii ( se khatna kya. ''ham se Quteba ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Mughira ne bayan kya aur unse abu-Zinaad ne ( بالقدوم‏‏ . Mina ( ) tashdeed ke sath bayan kya ( ."
6299,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki umr kya thi? kaha ke un dinon mera khatna ho chuka tha aur Arab logon ki aadat thi jab tak ladka jawaanii ke qareeb na hota uska khatna na kartey they.
6300,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to mera khatna ho chuka tha.
6301,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se jisne qism khaaii aur kaha ke laat w uzzaa ki qism , to phir wo ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahey aur jisne apne sathi se kaha ke aao juwa khelein to usey sadqa kar dena chahiye ''"
6302,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane main apne hathon se aik ghar banaya taake barish se hifazat rahe aur dhoop se saaya hasil ho. Allah ki makhlooq mein se kisi ne us kaam mein meri madad nahi ki. malum hua ke zarurat ke laaiq ghar banaanaa durust hai.
6303,Allah ki qism Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad na maine koi iint kisi iint par rakhi aur na koi baagh lagaya. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke jab maine iska zikr ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke kuchh gharaanon ke samney kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Allah ki qism unhon-ne ghar banaya tha. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine kaha phir ye baat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ghar banaaney se pahley kahi hogi.
